summary: Has anyone else noticed that Jamie Lannister's appearance has started to match that of Arthur Dayne's?
title: Has anyone else noticed that Jamie Lannister's appearance has started to match that of Arthur Dayne's?
body:
Like at the start of the series Jamie looked like Prince Charming from Shrek 2,

Pretty to look at but a real douche nozzle when he opens his mouth. But unlike Prince Charming Jamie has come to accept hard truths about himself and realises that he no longer wants to be known as just the Kingslayer (which is bullshit that people ostracizes him for killing a friggin’ madman and saving millions of lives) and so the longer he walks on the road to redemption the more he starts to resemble the man that he used to and still admires to this day.

Or I’m just looking too much into this, I saw the physical similarities and had to comment my own thoughts on it :D lol
